Fortress Real Estate (Asia) GK
hired  Douglas Smith  as a managing director to oversee its
property investment advisory business, according to three
people familiar with the situation.  Smith, 46, former head of real estate financing at
Deutsche Bank AG in Tokyo, joined Fortress Real Estate in
Tokyo on Oct. 1, the people said on condition of anonymity
